reviewText: Excellent movie and the early racing footage is very nice.
Good History lesson. done well worth watching. I enjoyed it and seeing the old motorcycles in action. I bought all the versions
This is part 3 of the series of motorcycle racing with emphasis on races in England and Europe.  Covers the moderm period.

Incredible DVD, period footage, great commentary by period racers, buy all three (3) DVDs to see the History of Motorcycle racing from the early 1900's untill present day. I watch these over and over in my garage while working on vintage bikes...
